author: Warhammer
description:
Hive Fleet Typhon are a hyper-predatory brood of Tyranids, often emerging to feast on worlds already weakened by war, famine, and disasters. There're rumours about these xenos cannibalising other Hive Fleets, so hopefully you can paint them up fast before they eat each other!
Here’s a list of the paints we used in today’s video:

Contrast:
Doomfire Magenta  

Base:
Corvus Black 
Phoenician Purple 
Screamer Pink 
The Fang
Tuskgor Fur 
Zandri Dust

Layer:
Blue Horror 
Dark Reaper
Emperor's Children 
Evil Sunz Scarlet 
Fenrisian Grey
Russ Grey 
Skavenblight Dinge
Word Bearers Red

Shade:
Agrax Earthshade
Drakenhof Nightshade 

Technical:
Astrogranite 
Lahmian Medium 

Brushes:
M Layer
M Shade

If you're new to painting, our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials playlist hosts an array of beginner-friendly videos to help you get started.
